ONE ON ONE ELIMINATION TOURNAMENT:  A challenge event in which PC's will
duel to their deaths in a small arena pit.  All challenges will be between
PC's of the same approximate level.  The challenges events will continue
in heat fashion until there is a winner and a runner-up.  Deaths will not
involve experience gains or losses and their will be no looting of
corpses.  Players may choose their competing characters from any of their
existing PC's.  Any class may participate in this event.  All competitors
will meet at the Challenge Events Contestant's Lounge in the area above
Grimhaven Center Square unless another place is designated on the
Tournament Board or by mail. 
